videos.headline: Wyoming opens the scoring with long TD run
videos.description: Brian Hill runs 56 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Wyoming increases lead after Hill's 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Brian Hill runs 2 yds for a TD as Wyoming now leads 14-3

videos.headline: Nevada closes gap with TD run
videos.description: Ty Gangi fakes hand off and runs 17 yds for a TD to cut Wyoming lead to 14-10

videos.headline: Wyoming goes up 21-10 after TD run
videos.description: Josh Allen rushes 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Wyoming trick play works for TD
videos.description: WR Austin Conway takes the hand off and passes to wide open QB Josh Allen in the endzone for a TD

videos.headline: Nevada answers back with TD run
videos.description: James Butler runs 9 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Hill finds the end zone again to increase Wyoming's lead
videos.description: Brian Hill was a beast on the ground for Wyoming, adding his third touchdown of the night to increase Wyoming's lead over Nevada to 35-20.

videos.headline: Nevada scores again with 27-yd TD pass
videos.description: Ty Gangi throws over the middle to Jarred Gipson for 27-yd TD

videos.headline: Wyoming TD opens up 42-27 lead
videos.description: Josh Allen keeps the ball and runs up middle for 7 yd TD

videos.headline: Nevada adds late TD
videos.description: James Butler dives in from 1-yd out for TD

videos.headline: Breakdown of Wyoming victory over Nevada
